ttps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sam-Fender-performing-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sam-Fender-performing-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sam-Fender-performing-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sam-Fender-performing-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Sam-Fender-performing-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Sam-Fender">山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）</a>的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-people-watching-review-3840019">《 People Watch》（People Watch）</a>正朝着第一名的位置，目前已经超出了英国前十名中的其余组合。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-people-watching-review-3840019">Sam Fender  - “观看人”评论：反光和敏锐的独立摇滚乐</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/sam-fender-people-watching-number-1-album-midweek/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方排行榜</a>，North Shields本地人正迅速努力成为他最近发行的第三张专辑的官方第一张专辑。 2月21日发布的“观看者”在短短三天后已经获得了2025年最大的开幕周。</p><p> Fender目前正在超越前十名中的其余与专辑相结合，其中80,000台已经发生了变化。预计“观看的人”将加入他的2019年首次亮相“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/sam-fender-hypersonic-missiles-review-2546624">Hypersonic导弹</a>”和2021年的“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">十七岁</a>”作为排行榜的LP。 </p><figure id="attachment_3812392" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812392" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812392" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）“观看”专辑插图。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg