rrell），</a><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-penguin">科林·法雷尔（Colin Farrell</a> ）赢得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-batman-review-robert-pattinson-3171137">蝙蝠侠</a>分拆系列企鹅的奖项。</em></p><p>当晚的其他地方，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timothee-chalamet">蒂莫西·查拉梅特（TimothéeChalamet）</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-dylan">鲍勃·迪伦（Bob Dylan）</a>传记片《<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/a-complete-unknown">完全未知》</a>中扮演了他的出色表现。</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/timothee-chalamet-says-hes-inspired-by-daniel-day-lewis-in-quest-for-greatness-during-sag-speech-3840717">他还说，他</a>在演讲中受到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-day-lewis">丹尼尔·戴·刘易斯（Daniel Day-Lewis）</a>的启发。</p><p>当晚的其他获奖者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/conclave-review-pope-ralph-fiennes-stanley-tucci-3815998"><i>Cendave</i></a>的演员，他在电影中获得了杰出表现的胜利，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/demi-moore">Demi Moore</a>则赢得了女演员的出色表现，赢得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-substance"><em>杰出的表现</em></a>。您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sag-awards-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-winners-3840664" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查看获奖者的完整列表。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harrison-ford">哈里森·福特（Harrison Ford）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/watch-harrison-ford-crash-shrinking-co-star-jessica-williams-sag-awards-monologue-3840761">在SAG颁奖典礼和新女孩Zooey Deschanel和Max Greenfield在颁奖典礼上的缩水杰西卡·威廉姆斯（Jessica Williams）在颁奖典礼上也被他的<em>缩小的</em>联合主演杰西卡·威廉姆斯（Jessica Williams</a> ）嘲笑，并在仪式上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/watch-new-girl-stars-zooey-deschanel-and-max-greenfield-reunite-at-sag-awards-2025-3840775"><em>团聚</em>了</a>，并为<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/only-murders-in-the-building"><em>仅在建筑物中的谋杀案</em></a>颁发了最佳喜剧系列合奏奖。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/andrew-scott-recalls-kidney-stones-agony-at-sag-awards-ceremony-3840825">安德鲁·斯科特（Andrew Scott）邮报（Andrew Scott）在SAG颁奖典礼上回忆起肾结石“痛苦”颁奖典礼上</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.